Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.46,TEXT,,0,0,0,,龍種 接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.28,TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:21.98,TEXT,,0,0,0,,可哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:23.30,TEXT,,0,0,0,,可哥——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:07.50,TEXT,,0,0,0,,捕捉敵軍反應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:08.70,TEXT,,0,0,0,,蓋倫級1
